description: **Price Improvement" and exclusive access to the spacious yard & your own private balcony! Summer awaits at 31 Mercer!  Don’t miss this stunning condo in the heart of South Boston’s vibrant Telegraph Hill. Spread across 2 spacious floors, this beautifully designed home offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The 1st floor features a sleek, modern kitchen with Caesarstone countertops, Alvic Luxe cabinetry, Fisher & Paykel appliances, & a new Wolf range. The open-concept living and dining area flows effortlessly to the backyard, creating an ideal setup for indoor-outdoor living. A dramatic two-story exposed brick staircase bathed in natural light leads to the 2nd floor, where you’ll find the luxurious primary suite,  2 custom closets and a spa-inspired en suite bath featuring heated floors & a floating double vanity. 2 additional bedrooms, a stylish full bath, & in-unit laundry round out the upper level. Close to beaches, parks, restaurants & public transit, this is Southie living at its' best!

exclusions: Tv Brackets In The Living Room And Bedroom With The Treadmill.
